---
import { ArrowLeft } from "lucide-react";
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>iOS Audio Troubleshooting | Baque Fácil</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="page-shell">
      <a class="back-link" href="/">
        <ArrowLeft aria-hidden="true" size={18} />
        All rhythms
      </a>

      <header class="page-header compact">
        <p class="eyebrow">iOS audio</p>
        <h1>Can't hear sound?</h1>
        <p>Follow these checks in order on iPhone or iPad.</p>
      </header>

      <section class="help-steps" aria-label="iOS audio troubleshooting steps">
        <ol>
          <li>
            <h2>Turn Silent Mode off</h2>
            <p>
              Use the Ring/Silent switch, Action Button, or Control Center for your device.
              Make sure the bell is not muted.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2>Turn the volume up</h2>
            <p>
              Keep this page open, then press the physical volume up button until media volume
              is audible.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2>Start audio from the Play button</h2>
            <p>
              iOS often requires a direct tap before web audio can start. Tap Play once, wait for
              samples to load, then tap Restart if needed.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2>Check Bluetooth and AirPlay</h2>
            <p>
              Open Control Center and confirm audio is not routed to headphones, a speaker, or
              another AirPlay device.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h2>Reload and try again</h2>
            <p>
              Refresh the page, keep Silent Mode off, and press Play again. If one rhythm is
              quiet, return to the rhythm list and try another page.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
